trans-unit.source: The type of elements in the queue.
trans-unit.target: O tipo dos elementos na fila.

trans-unit.source: Represents an immutable first-in, first-out collection of objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção imutável de objetos primeiro a entrar, primeiro a sair.

trans-unit.source: **NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
trans-unit.target: **Pacote NuGet**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">sobre coleções imutáveis e como instalá-las</see>)

trans-unit.source: Because <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601> is immutable, when you change <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601> using methods such as <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601.Dequeue%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601.Enqueue%2A>, a new queue will be returned with the changes applied and the original queue remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Porque <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601> é imutável, quando você alterar <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601> usando métodos como <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601.Dequeue%2A> ou <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.IImmutableQueue%601.Enqueue%2A>, uma nova fila será retornada com as alterações sejam aplicadas e a fila original permanece inalterada.

trans-unit.source: Returns a new queue with all the elements removed.
trans-unit.target: Retorna uma nova fila com todos os elementos removidos.

trans-unit.source: Removes the first element in the immutable queue, and returns the new queue.
trans-unit.target: Remove o primeiro elemento na fila imutável e retorna a nova fila.

trans-unit.source: The new immutable queue with the first element removed.
trans-unit.target: A nova fila imutável com o primeiro elemento removido.

trans-unit.source: Adds an element to the end of the immutable queue, and returns the new queue.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um elemento ao final da fila imutável e retorna a nova fila.

trans-unit.source: The new immutable queue with the specified element added.
trans-unit.target: A nova fila imutável com o elemento especificado adicionado.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether this immutable queue is empty.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se essa fila imutável está vazia.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if this queue is empty; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se essa fila está vazia. Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the element at the beginning of the immutable queue without removing it.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o elemento no início da fila imutável sem removê-lo.

trans-unit.source: The element at the beginning of the queue.
trans-unit.target: O elemento no início da fila.
